trans-unit.source: Defines endpoint or contract behaviors that can export custom metadata.
trans-unit.target: Definerer sluttpunktet eller kontrakten virkemåter som kan eksportere egendefinerte metadata.

trans-unit.source: To modify and extend the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) exported by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> objects, implement the IWsdlExportExtension interface on an endpoint, contract, or operation behavior (an object that implements either <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior>) and add the behavior to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Endre for å utvide Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) eksportert ved <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>objekter, implementere grensesnittet IWsdlExportExtension på en endepunktet, kontrakt eller operasjonen virkemåte (et objekt som implementerer enten <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior>, eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior>) og legge til virkemåten til den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A>, eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint.Behaviors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>

trans-unit.source: In addition, you can also implement IWsdlExportExtension on a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg kan du også implementere IWsdlExportExtension <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > IWsdlExportExtension implementations are never invoked if they are implemented as an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceBehavior>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > IWsdlExportExtension implementeringer aldri startes hvis de implementeres som et <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceBehavior>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceBehavior>

trans-unit.source: IWsdlExportExtension does not export custom policy assertions even though [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] exports custom binding policy assertions to the appropriate element inside WSDL.
trans-unit.target: IWsdlExportExtension eksporterer ikke egendefinerte policydeklarasjon selv om [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] eksporterer egendefinert binding policydeklarasjon til det aktuelle elementet i WSDL.

trans-unit.source: If you want to export custom policy assertions, implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> interface.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil eksportere egendefinerte policydeklarasjon implementere den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension>grensesnittet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: The metadata publication process begins by calling <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName> which in turn calls <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> for each endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Metadata publikasjonen prosessen begynner ved å kalle <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>som kaller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for hvert endepunkt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The endpoint is exported by first exporting its contract.When exporting a contract the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter?displayProperty=fullName> calls the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method on all IWsdlExportExtension implementations on the contract, and operation behaviors for that contract.
trans-unit.target: Endepunktet eksporteres ved første eksporterer kontrakten. Når du eksporterer en kontrakt den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter?displayProperty=fullName>kall av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName>-metoden på alle IWsdlExportExtension implementeringer i kontrakten, og operasjonen virkemåter for denne kontrakten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Operations that use wildcard actions are not exported in metadata, so IWsdlExportExtension implementations on operation behaviors for these operations are not exported.
trans-unit.target: Operasjoner som bruker jokertegn handlinger eksporteres ikke i metadataene, slik at IWsdlExportExtension implementeringer på operasjonen virkemåter for disse operasjonene ikke eksporteres.

trans-unit.source: After exporting the contract, the port and binding are exported and exported policy expressions are attached.
trans-unit.target: Når du har eksportert kontrakten, port og bindingen eksporteres og eksporteres policy uttrykk er koblet.

trans-unit.source: Both the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A> and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> methods provide access to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> so that IWsdlExportExtension implementations can report recoverable errors and warnings through the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Både den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A>metoder gir tilgang til den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>slik at IWsdlExportExtension implementeringer kan rapportere ugjenopprettbar feil og advarsler via den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: The context objects passed into both methods provide convenient mappings from exported WSDL elements to properties of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> objects.
trans-unit.target: Context-objekter som ble sendt til begge metodene gir praktisk tilordninger fra eksporterte WSDL-elementer egenskapene til <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>objekter.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>

trans-unit.source: If an IWsdlExportExtension implementation throws an exception on export, the generated metadata is in an inconsistent state and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> object should be discarded.
trans-unit.target: Om implementering av IWsdlExportExtension oppstår det et unntak for eksport, genererte metadataene er i en inkonsekvent tilstand og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>objektet må forkastes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Custom export extension must run after the built-in serializer populates the service description.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Egendefinerte eksport filtypen må kjøre etter innebygde serialiseringen fyller ut tjenestebeskrivelsen.

trans-unit.source: Writes custom Web Services Description Language (WSDL) elements into the generated WSDL for a contract.
trans-unit.target: Skriver egendefinerte Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) elementer i genererte WSDL for en kontrakt.

trans-unit.source: The ExportContract method is called when the metadata export system is exporting the contract.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ExportContract kalles når metadata eksport systemet eksporterer kontrakten.

trans-unit.source: Only contract and operation behaviors implementing <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension> get the ExportContract call.
trans-unit.target: Bare kontrakt og operasjon virkemåter implementere <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>får ExportContract-telefon.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: All behaviors implementing <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension> get the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> call.
trans-unit.target: Alle virkemåter implementere <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>Hent den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A>kall.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>

trans-unit.source: Use the `context` parameter to modify the WSDL to be exported.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av `context` parameteren til å endre WSDL eksporteres.

trans-unit.source: For an example, see the Example section.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se et eksempel kan du se delen eksempel.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"></xref> that exports the contract information.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"> </xref> som eksporterer Kontraktsinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: Provides mappings from exported WSDL elements to the contract description.
trans-unit.target: Gir tilordninger fra eksporterte WSDL-elementer i kontrakten beskrivelsen.

trans-unit.source: Writes custom Web Services Description Language (WSDL) elements into the generated WSDL for an endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Skriver egendefinerte Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) elementer i genererte WSDL for et sluttpunkt.

trans-unit.source: Implement the ExportEndpoint method to modify the WSDL exported for an endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Implementere metoden ExportEndpoint for å endre WSDL eksporteres for et sluttpunkt.

trans-unit.source: This method is called after the contract has been exported by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles når kontrakten har blitt eksportert av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension.ExportContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"></xref> that exports the endpoint information.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter"> </xref> som eksporterer Endepunktinformasjonen for.

trans-unit.target: Gir tilordninger fra eksporterte WSDL-elementer i endpoint beskrivelsen.
